Description: Replace FMOD Ex with SDL_mixer + software FFT spectrum analysis
 Replace the proprietary FMOD Ex library with the free SDL2_mixer library.
 Spectrum analysis (used for visual sync) is implemented using a Cooley-Tukey
 FFT with a Hann window on the PCM stream captured via Mix_SetPostMix().
 Engine.cpp is updated to call Mix_Init/Mix_Quit when EAPI_SDL_Mixer is set.
 main.cpp passes EAPI_SDL_Mixer so SDL_INIT_AUDIO is initialised correctly.
